  "title": "Salesmen",
  "html_content": "<main class=\"SuperHubDoc3Z-1XSVTg-Q1 rm-Guides\" id=\"content\"><div class=\"SuperHubDoc-container2RY1FPE4Ewze rm-Container rm-Container_flex\"><article class=\"SuperHubDoc-article3ArTrEavUTKg rm-Article rm-Guides-SuperHub\"><div class=\"grid-container-fluid\" id=\"content-container\"><section class=\"content-body grid-75\"><div class=\"rm-Markdown markdown-body rm-Markdown markdown-body ng-non-bindable\" data-testid=\"RDMD\" style=\"margin-left:31px\"><h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"view-order-details\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">View Order details</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to View Order details\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#view-order-details\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>To view all sales orders delivered to the customers associated with you, you can follow the steps below:</li>\n<li>Tap on <strong>Orders</strong> tab</li>\n<li>All sales orders delivered to the customers with whom you associate will be listed on <strong>Sales Orders</strong> sub tab</li>\n<li>To view the details of an order, you can simply tap on the corresponding order code</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"500\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/fd41d53-View_Orders.gif\" title=\"View Orders.gif\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>To search for a specific order, you can tap on the icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-search\"></i> on the top toolbar, then input the order code into the search bar. The app will filter and return the order which has that order code</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"404\" class=\"img border\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/ef69803-Untitled_Project.gif\" title=\"Untitled Project.gif\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"create-sales-orders\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Create Sales orders</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Create Sales orders\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#create-sales-orders\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"embed embed_hasImg\"><div class=\"embed-media\"></div></div>\n<ul>\n<li>If you have been assigned the permission to create sales orders on behalf of the customers which you manage, you can do so by following the below steps:</li>\n<li>Tap on <strong>Orders</strong> tab</li>\n<li>On this tab, tap on the orange <i class=\"fa-regular fa-plus-circle\"></i> icon, then tap on <strong>New Order</strong> icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-pencil\"></i></li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/0ecc81d-New_Order_button.png\" title=\"New Order button.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>You will be directed to the <strong>Create Order</strong> screen</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/3f87764-Create_Order_Screen.png\" title=\"Create Order Screen.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h3 class=\"heading heading-3 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"input-general-order-information\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Input general order information</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Input general order information\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#input-general-order-information\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tap on the text <strong>Select</strong> below the text <strong>Customer</strong>, you will be navigated to the <strong>Select Customer</strong> screen, where you can choose the customer</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/8ece9a3-Select_Customer.png\" title=\"Select Customer.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>You can swipe the customer list up and down to find the appropriate customer. You can also tap on the icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-search\"></i>, then input the name of the customer into the search bar to quickly filter out the appropriate customer</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/49237d9-Search_Cus.png\" title=\"Search Cus.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>After selecting the customer, tap on the icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-calendar-o\"></i> below the text <strong>Sale order date</strong> to select the date on which the order being created will be performed</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Next, consequently tap on <strong>Start time frame</strong> and <strong>End time frame</strong> to specify the time window on during which the order being created has to be performed on the date selected above</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/f709d67-Date.png\" title=\"Date.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>If the customer doesn't require a time window, you don't need to input anything into these fields</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"heading heading-3 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"input-product-information\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Input product information</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Input product information\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#input-product-information\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tap on the icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-plus\"></i> on the row <strong>Product</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/f57cc6c-Product_Button.png\" title=\"Product Button.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>You will be navigated to the <strong>Select Product</strong> screen</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/ab7ad41-Select_Product.png\" title=\"Select Product.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>You can swipe the product list up and down to find the appropriate product. You can also tap on the icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-search\"></i>, then input the name of the product into the search bar to quickly filter out the appropriate product. After finding the correct product, tap on that product to add it to the order</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/e17b285-Select_Product.png\" title=\"Select Product.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>If you incorrectly input the wrong product, tap on the trash bin icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-trash\"></i> to remove the product</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/43d995b-Trash_Bin.png\" title=\"Trash Bin.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>After selecting the product, you will be redirected back to the <strong>Create Order</strong> screen. Here you will have to specify the quantity of the whole case and/or quantity of single items for the selected product, by tapping on the corresponding numbers next to the texts <strong>Case</strong> and <strong>Item</strong>, input the correct case/single item quantity on the pop-out numeric keypad, then tap on <strong>Done</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/2ac846c-20200825_162603.png\" title=\"20200825_162603.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>If you incorrectly input the quantity, you can tap on the plus and minus icons <i class=\"fa-regular fa-plus-square-o\"></i> and <i class=\"fa-regular fa-minus-square-o\"></i> to increase/decrease the quantity as you wish. You can also tap directly on the numbers input earlier and input the new numbers</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/63d6c32-Quantity.png\" title=\"Quantity.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>If there are discount/promotion campaigns applied to the selected customer/product, the detail discount/promotion effect will be listed out under <strong>Discount</strong> and <strong>Promotions</strong> sections</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>The total value of the order will automatically be calculated and displayed on the orange <strong>Total</strong> section at the bottom of the screen</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/00863bb-Total.png\" title=\"Total.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<h3 class=\"heading heading-3 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"submit-order-to-the-order-approver\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Submit order to the order approver</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Submit order to the order approver\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#submit-order-to-the-order-approver\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>After inputting all necessary information of the order, if you are sure that the information is correct, you can submit the order to the order approver on Web app by tapping on the text <strong>Create</strong> on top of the screen</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/ac16c3e-20200825_162926.png\" title=\"20200825_162926.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>The order will immediately be submitted to the order approver</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"edit-submitted-orders\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Edit submitted orders</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Edit submitted orders\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#edit-submitted-orders\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>After the orders have been submitted, if the order approver has yet to approve/reject the order, then you can still edit those orders (If you have been assigned the permission to edit Orders)</li>\n<li>To edit Orders, follow the steps below:</li>\n<li>Tap on the Order code of the order which you want to edit</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>On the <strong>Order Detail</strong> screen, tap on the icon <i class=\"fa-regular fa-pencil\"></i> on top of the screen. Then you will be able to edit the information of that order</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/714f9c4-Edit_Order.png\" title=\"Edit Order.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>After making necessary changes, tap on the text <strong>Save</strong> to save the order</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"416\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/1a59e54-Save_Edit.png\" title=\"Save Edit.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span></div><div class=\"UpdatedAt\"><p class=\"DateLine\"><i class=\"icon icon-watch\"></i>Updated<!-- --> <!-- -->about 1 month ago<!-- --> </p></div><hr class=\"NextStepsDivider\"/><div class=\"WhatsNext-wrapper3DTnpcPqKoHg\"><div class=\"rm-Markdown markdown-body WhatsNext-description1zZyZLPCGmaa WhatsNext-description_empty1Hh8M1AKGhbW\" data-testid=\"RDMD\"></div><ul><li><a class=\"WhatsNext-link\" href=\"https://docs.abivin.com/docs/vrp-in-house-fleet-salesmen-web\" target=\"blank\">Salesmen (Web app)</a><span class=\"IconWrapper Icon-wrapper2z2wVIeGsiUy\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"Icon Icon3_D2ysxFZ_ll Icon-svg2Lm7f6G9Ly5a icon\" data-name=\"arrow-up-right\" fill=\"none\" role=\"img\" style=\"--icon-color:inherit;--icon-size:inherit;--icon-stroke-width:2px\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path class=\"icon-stroke-width\" d=\"M7 17 17 7M7 7h10v10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></span></li></ul></div></section><section class=\"content-toc grid-25\"></section></div><div class=\"ModalWrapper\" id=\"tutorialmodal-root\"></div></article></div></main>",
